{"tid":1432663,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中移動記者會派鐳射筆　董事長：是否攻擊性武器看你怎麼用","createTime":"2019-08-08T09:38:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T05:31:16.000Z","uid":20933,"like":934,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":104,"replies":[{"pid":"1d58b61e5ff7ee1ddf7da5996a238b7514fa6d66","tid":1432663,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:38:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190808/large/1565254073_3478.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190808%2Flarge%2F1565254073_3478.jpg&h=fbba1328&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190808/large/1565253940_bed9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190808%2Flarge%2F1565253940_bed9.jpg&h=d9092798&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9bc205a5d6e418299352aacfebb8da5c52a69aa1","tid":1432663,"uid":71433,"like":178,"dislike":5,"score":173,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:39:19.000Z","msg":"反了"},{"pid":"216d54f902e6078a68dfd1ecbd05559eee5b8b23","tid":1432663,"uid":20933,"like":247,"dislike":2,"score":245,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:39:44.000Z","msg":"浸大學生會會長因購買鐳射筆，被警方以藏有攻擊性武器拘捕，事件持續發酵。今日中移動（941）公佈業績，記者會時疑「抽水」，向在場傳媒派送激光筆，根據鐳射筆包裝說明，不可直視激光光束及將光束瞄準任何人眼睛。<br />\n<br />\n中移動執行董事兼董事長楊杰指，鐳射筆是不是攻擊性武器，「關鍵看你怎麼用」，若是攻擊警方則會是武器，用在工作上則是好東西。在場的職員隨即解畫，指鐳射筆早在年初時就準備好，而中移動過去一直有向記者提供小禮品，今次的鐳射筆有7個功能，希望不要有單一功能和現時的事件聯想在一起。"},{"pid":"75ce37867ee9684a0e4852c85a4b6c1c71b92713","tid":1432663,"uid":20933,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:39:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190808/59910087\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190808%2F59910087&d=g7cViP25SqI%2F%2FE6cIGpO7%2FUUj30esm9w7dCaRgXMgeE%3D&h=dca512cd\" data-ef-url=\"https://